girl_dialog: Humans suffer so much frustration and betrayal in romance. I wonder if they still believe in love.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Good answer! Doesn't love appear precious because of many hardships?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Your tone makes you sound bitter and jaded. There's no need for that. With me at your side, your luck with love will be much better.

girl_dialog: Do you have a crush on a special someone? Would you like for me to use one of my arrows to make her fall in love with you?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Right? After all, if gods are so different from humans that they can't share a deep love with them, I would rather not be a god!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: ... After all, humans have short lifespans. And, sadly, their love dies with them.

girl_dialog: Do you have a crush on a special someone? Would you like for me to use one of my arrows to make her fall in love with you?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: If you don't tell me who it is, then I'll write your name on an arrow and shoot it out blindly! Do you really want to leave it up to chance?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: So which lucky girl will my arrow of love strike? Wait... This arrow seems to be targeting me?!

girl_dialog: Humans always think that power and money can buy them anything. But that's not the case with love.
switch_2: How do you know when you've found true love?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I make it my mission to ruin love rooted in greed. Will you stay at my side and help?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You know its true love when you're willing to give up everything for it, including the power to rule the world.

girl_dialog: Are you good at archery?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? That's great! I'm a bit tired of being the god of love and need a break. I'm looking for someone to take my place for a while
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Do you want me to give you private lessons? Just grab my hand and draw back the bowstring. ...Oh, why is your other hand touching me there?

girl_dialog: Being a god of love is also quite boring. I also want to have an unforgettable date!
switch_2: Who do you want to date?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I wasn't expecting you to ask me so suddenly! I don't know what to say...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Anyone would be fine... Although, a date with you would be nice.

girl_dialog: I like lilies very much. It can symbolize purity and loyalty more than ever in the world.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: That's just the way it is! No matter how pleasant your words are, I won't be happy with the praise from mortals!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are different from those who love flowers with beautiful colors, which surprised me a lot..

girl_dialog: According to prophecy, I will marry a very powerful person who lusts after women.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It seems that you are a person who does not believe in fate. It has been a long time since no mortal dared to fight against fate.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: For your sake, you better hope that person isn't you. Whoever I marry will suffer horribly.

girl_dialog: Want to visit my private garden? Even if the end of the world comes, I have a quiet place of my own.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: There's no one else here. Just relax and enjoy this time alone together.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Although there are only two of us! But this is just a personal invitation, don't think too much!

girl_dialog: The flames of war give my flowers an especially attractive glow.
switch_2: I wish you good luck and prosperity.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I'm never soft on the battlefield. But if you want me to treat the enemy with kindness, I won't object.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Haha... Many people have already said this to me and followed me onto the battlefield. Would you like to know their stories?

girl_dialog: Since I lost my divine power and memory, it seems that the whole world doesn't care about me anymore.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: What are you talking about! I don't... don't care if a mortal admires me!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Haha...Yes, what this world prizes power. Would you help me regain some of my power by serving as my sword and shield?

girl_dialog: Mortals are pitifully weak. Yet history has proven their resilience time and time again.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You are different from everyone else! You are the only one I have ever admired. That is why I have chosen you and only you.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: The gods are always fighting amongst themselves. Yet, I'm astounded that you have managed to unite even opposing gods under one banner.

girl_dialog: I still have a fear of flying. Maybe I should give up using these wings?
switch_1: You need to face your fears.
switch_2: Giving up is not a bad thing.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You're right. I will continue trying to overcome my fear.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Whether or not I can fly doesn't matter. Seeing you gives me courage.

girl_dialog: According to some, ignorant people are often fearless. Do you agree that bravery is rooted in ignorance?
switch_1: There may be some truth to that.
switch_2: If so, such bravery seems reckless.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I think so, too. When heroes know they might fall in battle, it can fill them with fear.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Yes, sometimes that is true. But such recklessness comes at a heavy cost.

girl_dialog: Truth is deceptively alluring. Though we know we will never understand it, we still pursue it with voracious curiosity.
switch_1: Wisdom can only be found in truth.
switch_2: It's not bad to be naive.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Unfortunately, my bravery precludes such wisdom, for I rarely think things through. I am often blinded by my confidence.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Some things grow more confusing the more you think about them. Regardless, it is still good to ponder such things.

girl_dialog: Wonderful art is like an clever invention. Both are products of great imagination and creativity. Don't you agree?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Therefore, a good artist should also be a good inventor. I always dream to be such a person!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: My artificial wings are a spectacularly beautiful invention! Aren't they the perfect example of artistic invention?

girl_dialog: Sculpture is a passion of mine. No matter my mood, it always calms me down.
switch_1: I want to see your works!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: My sculptures are a private affair since they are all body art based on myself. But for you, I'll make an exception.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Sculpture is best learned on your own, though I would be happy to be your model!

girl_dialog: I still can't figure out what distinguishes gods from the rest of creation...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Not necessarily. I have seen many human heroes in Greece. They are fully strong enough to compete with gods on the battlefield!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: There are many monsters and demons whose lifespans are nearly eternal, but they don't seem to be gods either.

girl_dialog: Do you like snowy winters?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I'm pleased that you enjoy that season. The cold often brings an icy calm to the land.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: People often associate cold with death. However, snow and ice are part of the world, and they are eternal.

girl_dialog: I used to spend a long time in my lair, and no one can understand that feeling of loneliness...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Many great human heroes have faced like this. They are surrounded by countless glory, but they are never understood by others.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I never thought I would be interested in a human being, but the days with you seem to be quite interesting.

girl_dialog: I don't agree with war, because war will always bring endless disasters to this world...
switch_2: There is always a reason for war.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Fortunately you think so. What the world needs is rationality and order, not chaos and destruction.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: But most of the reasons are unreasonable. I hope you can calmly think about the meaning of every battle like me.

girl_dialog: Want to know my sisters of the same race? They seem to have awakened in this disaster.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: She is the worst-tempered of our three sisters. She is very anxious but enthusiastic and refreshing, and she has a good relationship with humans.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: She has the brightest mind of our three sisters. There have been many bounty hunters to fight against her, but none of them have come back...

girl_dialog: Humans are eager for eternal life like gods. This is actually not difficult to do. Do you want to try it?
switch_1: I want to give it a try!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: The method is very simple. Freeze yourself, then you can have eternal youth like me. Isn't this wonderful?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Wise decision. Mankind may be able to obtain eternal life, but it may pay a greater price for it...

girl_dialog: Most humans think that I am just a cold and merciless god. Do you think so too?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Strange guy... Maybe this is why I am willing to open my heart in front of you...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I don't know...but so far, no one will accompany me like you all the time...

girl_dialog: You seem to be available. Would you like to spend a long night with this lonely lady?
switch_2: Uh, I'm afraid I have other things to do.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oh! So direct! ...But yes, it would be a date. I hope to share a lovely evening with you. We could make many pleasant memories.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmm... let me guess... You already have plans with another girl?

girl_dialog: Is it really that important for someone to tell the truth?
switch_2: I don't like to be lied to.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Since I created the world, I haven't seen many humans tell the truth. It's a pity.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh really? So... I love you. But is that the truth or a lie? Take a guess.

girl_dialog: Do you prefer day or night?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I envy humans for the time they spend in the afternoon sun, whether it be shopping, sunbathing, or strolling through the park with a lover.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: The night is full of mystery. It is the perfect time for two lovers to be alone... Anyway... Are you free tonight?

girl_dialog: In my opinion, humans worry too much about good and evil when deciding how to act. What really matters their intention and conviction.
switch_1: I think kindness is most important.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oh, really? Then we'll see if your kindness can save us from the disaster that's engulfed the world.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: That's pleasing to hear. I prefer strong individuals.

girl_dialog: When faced with a difficult decision, do you rely more on intuition or rational analysis?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: If you follow your instincts, what sort of trouble will the two of us get into tonight when we're alone in our room?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You may be calm and rational now, but we'll see how long that lasts in the presence of my seductive charm.

girl_dialog: Movies are one of the most wonderful inventions of human civilization. Do you love watching movies? Which do you prefer, comedy or tragedy?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Not surprising. The world is already full of tragedy. ...And speaking of tragedies, I hope you can stop the disaster that's engulfing the world today.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I'm shocked! Just don't watch too many of them. I don't want them to make you pessimistic.

girl_dialog: The moonlight is pretty tonight, isn't it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: From now on I will miss the moon that we saw today, and I hope you will not forget today's promise...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You don't need to answer me so quickly. I will wait until you complete your mission.

girl_dialog: I am not afraid of this war, I hope to end it with you.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Thank you for your trust in me all the time, and I will protect your back on the deadly battlefield.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Then at least allow me to pray to the moon for your safety every night before the war is over.

girl_dialog: I like gentle animals like rabbits very much, how about you?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: They like to get close to humans very much. They are so lovable guys...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmm... With your personality, you might prefer some fierce and wild guys, right?

girl_dialog: If one day, I have to go back to the moon, would you like to go with me?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: After this war is over, let's go back to my hometown together, where there will never be apocalypse and disaster.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I understand that you are in this world, maybe there are things you can never give up...

girl_dialog: I actually don't want to be a god, because eternal life is too heavy for me...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I should be grateful for meeting you. Maybe this is the greatest comfort that fate has given a lonely person.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Mortal people sigh for the short life. How can they understand the eternal loneliness...

girl_dialog: It's a boring and deserted night. When I was lonely in the past, I would always sing a nursery rhyme to relieve boredom.
switch_1: I want to hear you sing.
switch_2: Do you want me to sing it to you?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Then lie down on my lap, close your eyes and listen quietly. Wish you a good night...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, if it were you, I would be happy to listen.

girl_dialog: What do the battlefield horns inspire?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Well, next time show me your bravery on the battlefield.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Only those who have had their homeland invaded would understand.

girl_dialog: As long as I can fight, the enemy will never set foot inside the city gate.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You are very reassuring.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: So far, I have never let my Nordic companions down.

girl_dialog: There is always someone we want to protect. This is true for everyone.
switch_1: Who do you want to protect?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I refuse to answer, but... you will know in the future…
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Then, what about you? Who do you want to protect?

girl_dialog: Have you heard of Ragnarok?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I swear... Never let this happen again in this world.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, that's ok, you don't want to know how tragic the disaster was...

girl_dialog: You almost died in the previous battle! How can you be so reckless!
switch_2: The brave always have good luck.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I wasn't worried. I was just... pointing it out.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If you don't have my protection next time, then don't take risks like that again!

girl_dialog: I'm afraid it will be difficult to recover the divine power I lost...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: What do you mean... Are you willing to regain my strength with me?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You fool...

girl_dialog: You are too young to be a ruler! If I were you, I'd be desperate to gain experience and mature as quickly as possible.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You remind me of my youth. It was nice to reminisce on ages past.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I'm glad you're not short-tempered like me. Maybe you're a more suitable commander than I am.

girl_dialog: I see little distinction between gods and mortals. Gods are just more powerful versions of humans.
switch_2: But gods are immortal, and humans are not.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Therefore, as long as human beings continuously hone themselves, one day they will be able to reach the mighty state of gods!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: When it comes to eternal life, humans can achieve it either through prayer or magic. Just look at me! I'm the perfect example.

girl_dialog: War is glorious in its own way. I am not afraid of war at all, nor do I deny its importance.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It is worth dying on the battlefield for your own ideas and values. After all, isn't the greatest joy in life to think and act as one pleases?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I hope you can also find the meaning and value of your life on the battlefield, and fight for your own ideas!

girl_dialog: Do you think it is weird for a miko, or shrine maiden, to wear a samurai costume?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It's not weird to me either. It's the meaning behind it that's important. A miko must not only be wise and reverent, but she must also have the will of a samurai!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You won't think it strange when I prove to you on the battlefield that I am also a qualified warrior with an indomitable will!

girl_dialog: Ever since I was reincarnated in this world, I have spent each day thinking about eventually restoring the country of Yamatai.
switch_2: Do not tangle in the past.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I knew I could trust you! I look forward to seeing your talent and courage as a ruler!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If anyone else said this, I would never agree. I don't know why, but I always think you're right.

girl_dialog: Do you think I am too serious for a woman? Does it make me less feminine?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Good, because even the most feminine woman can have a strong and commanding side to her personality!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: When I'm with you, I worry about it more than I should admit.

girl_dialog: The more powerful the force, the more dangerous it is, and so is the storm...
switch_1: I will stay away from the storm.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Unlike most humans, you are more rational than I thought, and maybe it is a correct decision to cooperate with you.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Really? You are the 147th human to say this. Guess the fate of the last 146 guys?

girl_dialog: Only wisdom can control powerful forces, not anger. How do you think of it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I am very pleased to hear that you agree with my point of view, maybe you really have the ability to become the leader of the gods.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Anger will only make your head hot, but if you can control your own anger, you may also have powerful power.

girl_dialog: The war is simply boring. With the time for fighting and killing, it is better to study others.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: In a way, you are right. After defeating the group of idiots who came to crusade against me, my strength has indeed improved a lot.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: So how long will it take you to end this world war between the gods?

girl_dialog: Two sisters of my family seem to have awakened with this disaster...Although it was also in my expectation...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It's not a good thing for this grumpy guy to wake up. Surprisingly, she gets along well with humans...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If you're fine, don't mess with her. If she is in a bad mood, you may be frozen in ice for the rest of your life...

girl_dialog: Why do humans and gods like to entangle their identities so much... Gods and humans are indistinguishable from me.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: God also has birth and destruction, and he also needs to follow the rules of the world. God is not the truth, but just a strong existence.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: In my opinion, only those who want to become gods would say this. It seems that you are also an ambitious guy...

girl_dialog: Although I regard you as a competitor, I have to admit that I have a good impression of you...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: In addition to competitors. I am looking forward to the relationship with you in the future, that... a deeper relationship can also be...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are too slow! We have been working together for so long, haven't you noticed it...

girl_dialog: Ah...it's so boring! ! I really want to find a strong one to fight! !
switch_2: Are you in the next battle?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: no problem! This time I won't be like the last time, because I lost to you carelessly!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Is it finally my turn to play? ! Wait to see me burn the enemy into a barbecue! Hahaha!

girl_dialog: Are you asking about what I would do when I met an enemy? Of course, first persuade him to surrender! Roast him without surrendering!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Do I look like a merciful person? ! Nothing excites me more than defeating an enemy!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Even if it is a monster, it must be given a chance to solve the problem peacefully, although it is useless most of the time.

girl_dialog: War is no different from a game. It's just who gets out first, what do you think?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: As your companion, I am very happy to hear you, the commander-in-chief, agree with me, hum...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It's no surprise that when I stepped onto the battlefield of this world, I had no longer any nostalgia for life.

girl_dialog: Hmm... I noticed that the two sisters, just like me, have also awakened in this world...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: She is a wise and strategic guy, but if you really want to fight, she will definitely not be able to beat me!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: That cold guy is so boring, I can't stay by her side for a second!

girl_dialog: The reason why God owns the place not because he is powerful, but he has extraordinary courage and determination to die on the battlefield!
switch_2: What you think is too simple.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Therefore, as the commander of the gods, you must have courage stronger than them!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Thinking too complicated is meaningless. Without courage, how do you face the difficulties and fears on the way to becoming a god?

girl_dialog: Human cooking is really interesting. I have begun to understand the meaning of the phrase civilization begins with flames.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Didn't expect it? ! My craftsmanship is not inferior to your top human chefs!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmm... let me think... I like most of the dishes, but of course, the roast meats are my favorite! !

girl_dialog: It seems that even if I spared no effort, it is still difficult to make the sun of this world shine again...
switch_1: There is no need to blame yourself.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Indeed. Self-blame has no significance. As a symbol of light and hope, I need to cheer up again!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are right...Even if you were once the ruler of the sun, you still need to face the end of the world with your companions.

girl_dialog: I often recalled the days when I was in Takamagahara. Although there were constant troubles, they enriched my life.
switch_1: People need to face the future.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Sorry, I seem to be over-indulged in the passing time. I hope it didn't bother you.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: As you said, people expect to find a peaceful life like in the past, so we must end this disaster!

girl_dialog: Why do people have to use war to solve problems and contradictions? Doesn't this make the matter worse?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Anyway, I always believe that differences in ideas can be unified in a more peaceful way, not war.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I can understand the dilemma that needs to be resolved immediately in a crisis, but I still hope that you treat every war with caution.

girl_dialog: After going through this disaster, I must revive the former glory of Yamato god pedigree and bring peace to the gods!
switch_2: That sounds like a heavy burden.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: At that time, the Yamato gods will take the responsibility of maintaining peace, so the re will be no disputes anymore.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: But I will definitely complete this mission. Do you feel it? That's why destiny made me come to this world.

girl_dialog: Your clothes were damaged badly in the battle... Do you want me to make you a new one?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Although I live in a different era from you, I am very confident in my skills in spinning and designing clothes!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Although when I measure your height and measurements, you need to be frank with me, I think our relationship should be fine for that...

girl_dialog: Mortal people always fear death. In my opinion, death means tranquility free from emotion and eternal beauty...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Haha, when a person feels no fear of death, he will no longer have any weaknesses. You will soon understand...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are the most rational mortal I have ever met. Our future cooperation may become more interesting...

girl_dialog: Whoever it is, it is god or mortal, everyone needs to face the fate of destruction and vanishing...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Therefore, no matter it is mortal or gods, they should follow fate while they are alive and prepare for death...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh, really? I would like to see if you, as the spokesperson of death, can escape from me...

girl_dialog: Why do people always call my strategy a conspiracy? Is there any difference between good and evil in fighting strategies?
switch_1: I think there is no difference.
switch_2: I think there is a difference.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: A wise answer. A strategy is just a strategy, to differ them as good or evil is just a kind of rhetoric and excuse.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It seems that you are different from me. You are more willing to use your fists and strength to resolve conflicts... Should I praise your sense of glory?

girl_dialog: I never deny that I am a careerist. This messy world is so in need of order and unity!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You are right, but unfortunately, this sentence is only valid when the strong man is alive...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh, it's hard to believe that I would hear this from mortals. That's right, you will find that death is the fairest rule in the world.

girl_dialog: Is glory such an important thing to a soldier?
switch_1: At least I think it is.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes...see how many heroes lost their lives for glory. Death in this way is also an art...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Death will erase everything. Whatever how great the glory was made by the hero, it will fade away with the passing of admirers...

girl_dialog: Death is not horrible. What's terrible is that you have regrets for your life when you die.
switch_2: I have no regrets at all!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Look at your reaction...do you think that the biggest regret in life is the lack of a girl's company?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, look at the girls around you, see how they admire you. You really have no regrets in your life.

girl_dialog: Monsters are rampant in the underworld recently, which is very bad. Do you have time to solve the trouble with me together?
switch_1: I bet it's a mission with no return.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: With your strong power, you will return from any dangerous place. Of course, it is another matter of which way you come back, whether it is standing or lying down...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmm... you'd better put on the thickest armor before you leave, otherwise I don't guarantee that you will come back completely...

girl_dialog: Are you interested in judging the dead with me?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You made a sensible choice! When you go on my trial after you die, I promise you will know more...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Don't worry, it's much more fun than you think...especially when you kick the nasty guy down the abyss...

girl_dialog: War is meaningless. Destiny will not be changed just by a war...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I don't feel repulsion for war. The dead people caused by war can make my lonely palace bustling for months...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, let's make a bet and see if this doomsday can end with the war you lead.

girl_dialog: As a mortal, what do you think of me as a god of death?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Uh-hum, are you free tonight? Are you interested in experiencing the charming side of the god of death in my room?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It really disappoints me. It seems that I need to punish you tonight who doesn't understand the romance...

girl_dialog: War is an act of harming nature, and I will prevent it at any time.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Nature does sometimes bring disasters, but this is a destiny directed by heaven, not a man-made disaster.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Although you often fight on the battlefield, I know that everything you do is to end the war as soon as possible.

girl_dialog: It often takes several years to repair the cracks in the heavens, which needs to be patient...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I hope you don't get too impatient when you get along with girls. Girls get angry even more terrible than the heaven cracks...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh, is it? Then you must be very good at chasing girls. It takes a lot of patience to get along with girls...

girl_dialog: Conforming to nature is the most reasonable behavior. Everything and every rule in the world are originated from nature.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I am very pleased that you can agree. Everything has a destiny, and nature controls them all the time.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I certainly don't think other people can succeed, but if it is you... maybe there is a small possibility.

girl_dialog: Although I have lost part of my divine power, I don't regret it. It's just that nature needs me to return the power to it.
switch_1: Do you want to regain your divine power?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I appreciate your kindness, but there is no need to do so, because this is the destiny that nature wants me to face.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Haha... No mortal has ever said something like this to me...Do you know what it means?

girl_dialog: Do you ask me about my hobbies? I think I like raising cute animals and growing flowers.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Believe me, after experiencing countless adventures and excitement, you will feel that dull life is a kind of enjoyment.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Do you think so too?! Would you be interested in coming to my garden tonight to see the potted plants I plant?

girl_dialog: Even if I am the only one left in the world, I will fight for justice to the last second!
switch_1: I will be always at your side.
switch_2: Hope you can grant me courage.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Humph... Hope you can really have this consciousness. After all, justice requires extraordinary courage.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Courage comes from your consciousness. When your consciousness is unassailable, nothing can stop you on the battlefield.

girl_dialog: Do you want to know heaven? It seems to be nothing special for me, but at least there won't be any evil.
switch_1: Hope to go there and have a look.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I can send you to heaven right now, but there is no return. Do you want to have a try?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I don't know, but judging from the screams from the sulfur fiery pits of hell every day, it should be a very exciting place.

girl_dialog: War is the fastest way to destroy evil, but not the best way...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Do you think it is really the devil who destroys this world? Or it is the evil thoughts hidden in the hearts of people or gods?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I don't know either, but I'd rather say that I hope you can solve this problem one day.

girl_dialog: Lucifer... I am looking forward to what you will do with this evil and crafty guy after we catch her.
switch_1: I'll persuade her to work for me.
switch_2: What do you think I should do?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Are you kidding me? ! If it is true, I must give you a few punches to confirm that you are not dreaming!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I would be happy to find a choir to sing hymns to her every day for hundreds of years, until she can't stand then pleads guilty and repents.

girl_dialog: As the leader of the gods, you are still too young. In many cases, you lack the rationality to handle things like I do.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: As a commander of the gods, courage and rationality are all needed, but rationality is the prerequisite for all correct judgments!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: What... what are you going to do? ! The people around us.. They are watching us! I'm going to be angry if you don't let go!

girl_dialog: I was born for war and the eternal glory found only through victory on the battlefield!
switch_1: Wish you good luck in the war.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: So, when is the next battle? I am looking forward to fighting against powerful enemies.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: We will achieve glory in the name of Valhalla! I hope that we can be invincible under your command!

girl_dialog: You want to know what weapons I fight best with? I'm good with all weapons!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Because my body harbors the souls of many Valkyries, I can use all of their combat techniques.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: No problem! With your aptitude and perception, you can easily master all of these skills!

girl_dialog: I am never alone, for my body harbors the souls of all the Valkyries that came before me.
switch_2: Are they aligned with our goals?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I don't know, but I felt all of my sisters resonating when I arrived in response to your summons.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Of course we do. But when we disagree, I stop to meditate. Then, within my mind, we battle each other. When it is over, all of us listen to the winner.

girl_dialog: Ah, sorry, I was a bit distracted just now. In fact, I was thinking about your battle tactics.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Valkyries are excellent warriors, but unfortunately we are poor military advisors.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Based on our previous victories, your battle tactics have proven to be sound.

girl_dialog: Since being summoned to this world, my sisters and I have grown to miss our time in Valhalla.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes! It is a spectacular palace that is also the sanctuary of all the Nordic Valkyries.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Yep! If you want to experience blissful peace, you can visit my room tonight. I'm sure you'll enjoy your stay...

girl_dialog: Are you interested in letting me build an artifact for you, that is unparalleled in the world?
switch_1: Such a peaceful place must be blissful.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Well, it may take a long time to craft, maybe for two or three hundred years...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If you are unlucky, the artifact may bring curses. But don't worry, it won't kill you. At most, you will have nightmares for a few days...

girl_dialog: To be honest, sometimes I always feel that the weapons I built have caused some unnecessary wars.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: But if there are no weapons, how can a kind person resist the invasion of evil?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Perhaps you are right. Weapons should be used to defend our homeland, not to invade and pillage the weak.

girl_dialog: When you battle with enemies, which strategy do you prefer? Melee assault or long-range containment?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It is very similar to your brave and skillful character. Speed is precious in war. There is no more effective tactic than to quickly assault the enemies' weaknesses.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It surprised me. I never realized that your archery level is so high!

girl_dialog: Every piece of equipment needs to be polished day after day, at least I will not tolerate any mistakes.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I can boast to say that there have never been any problems with the weapons I have made so far!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Yes, a craftsman often needs to have the experience of building hundreds of equipment before he can become a master of a generation.

girl_dialog: Doomsday has always been the favorite stage of careerists and revolutionaries. Don't you think so?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I know you never let me down. There is no better opportunity to create a new order in doomsday.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, You can't shield it from me. You already have ambitions to command all the gods, right?

girl_dialog: No one has ever understood the real reason...why I must be the ruler of the world.
switch_2: I would like to hear you talk about it.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? Are you comforting me? But even if you just simply comfort me, I'm pretty happy...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah, after rule the world, even if I am a devil, I can stay with you justifiably every day, can't I?

girl_dialog: I can see that you are restless due to a hidden desire to me in the heart... isn't it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really, my little one? So why is it me that is talking to you intimately here, not other girls?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah...what an honest guy, are you interested in coming to my room tonight and spending a long night with me?

girl_dialog: The devil is just an identity. Whether it is an angel or devil, the one will always become a companion just as it should be.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes, I'm very interested in making friends with them, such as the guy named Michael...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It surprised me! I never thought you could really accept such extreme but wise advice!

girl_dialog: Do you know? Dancing on the battlefield is not only an art, but also a good way to improve soldier morale!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hmm...your figure is also suitable for dancing! Are you interested in learning from me?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hum...Dance is not only performance. If it is combined with the use of weapons, it can become a very deadly offensive method!

girl_dialog: There are still a few hours until the next battle. It's so boring. How about tossing a coin?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You are lucky! Give this special coin to you as a souvenir! Don't despise it, you will have good luck with it!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Unfortunately, it came down heads. It seems that as the goddess of victory, even if tossing a coin, I will never lose!

girl_dialog: As the goddess of victory, I am not the most powerful warrior, but the warriors can become powerful because of me.
switch_2: You are quite suitable to be an idol.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I will be proud of this. I look forward to supporting my companions as best as I can in future battles.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I... I actually had this idea a long time ago... I just...just too shy to tell others...

girl_dialog: Anyone who dares to break the law will inevitably face eternal punishment, all in the name of justice!
switch_1: There are imperfections in the law.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You're not wrong. But without law, the world would lose all sense of fairness and principle.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: That pleases me. As the commander of the gods, you must understand the importance of law. An army needs order.

girl_dialog: Many people complain about their bad luck. It suggests that fate is inevitable.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: The wicked will always stand trial for their evil acts. They can never escape the goddess of vengeance.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Humans are the most unbridled and conceited race I have ever seen. Perhaps this is what allows humans to change their fate.

girl_dialog: Even though I am the goddess of vengeance, I hope that one day there will be no more sinners in the world.
switch_1: I doubt that will ever happen.
switch_2: I will try my best to help you.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Justice has been difficult to reach since ancient times, but I will not shy away from trying. And because crime is an endless problem, my vengeance will also be endless.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I don't want to see you share my fate. Revenge and justice are heavy burdens. I would rather see you smile.

girl_dialog: If there is a chance, do you want to have the ability to turn the opponent into a stone at a glance?
switch_1: It's very effective against the enemy!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I want to get rid of this ability, because instead of improving combat power, I care more about not being able to face the person I like...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It seems that you already have a girl you like. If you have such skill, you can't look at her well.

girl_dialog: I like to read romance novels between different races. Will human beings mind the romance between different races?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hmm...well...then the next question is, do you mind the love between humans and the Gorgon...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah... but this seems to make me even more yearning for this forbidden love...

girl_dialog: What is popular among humans recently? If I also start to follow the trend, will humans accept me more?
switch_2: You already have a strong personality!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Are they? ! Then I want to know, what kind of fashion do young human girls like to wear at this time?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah... I'm embarrassed to hear that! It seems that inner and personality is the greatest charm...

girl_dialog: Compared to daytime, I prefer to come out to relax and feel the tranquility of the world after night falls...
switch_2: I'm still used to the daytime.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Are you interested in chatting with me tonight? Perhaps the wines from Crete can make us enjoy a wonderful evening.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Human beings were born in the dark, but yearn for the light. This is really an interesting thing...

girl_dialog: I used to feel helpless for losing my mighty divine power, but this is also the unpredictable nature of darkness.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes, maybe destiny also hopes that I will not interfere too much in the disputes in this world...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ahh.. no human beings have said this to me yet, but if you want, I am looking forward to spending time with you.

girl_dialog: As the messenger of the gods and the incarnation of the rainbow, lightning speed is my most proud advantage.
switch_1: Indeed, speed is precious in war..
switch_2: I feel like you will hit something.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes, you are right! Although my combat power is not the strongest, the most important thing in war is reconnaissance and communication!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It will never happen! If you don't believe me, I can fly with you and let you see it with your own eyes!

girl_dialog: I am working on magic that can turn painting into reality! What do you think?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Next time I will draw a sketch of you! In this way, our combat power can be doubled!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Are you interested in learning? I can teach you! But I have to make sure that your drawing skills are not too bad...

girl_dialog: The Chinese lute is an elegant oriental musical instrument. It always makes people feel peaceful...
switch_1: Can you teach me to play?
switch_2: Do you want to play it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: After this disaster is over, I will be happy to study the Chinese lute and music theory with you for the rest of the time.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: The performance of musical instruments requires a tranquil heart and an elegant atmosphere. If you want to listen, come to my room at night...

girl_dialog: War brings suffering, and even if the gods have eternal life, there will only be emptiness in the end.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: If it is you to lead the gods and quell the war, this day might come as soon as possible...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are right. Depression will only bury hope and determination. Instead of sighing, it is better to fight this doomsday destiny.

girl_dialog: Hi! Are you interested in signing a new contract with the cute and charming succubus idol?
switch_1: Didn't you just sign it yesterday?
switch_2: I feel that there is a conspiracy...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Well... As hell's number one idol and Lucifer's leading pioneer, Lilith's recent performance is not enough!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Stop being suspicious! If you are willing to sign, Lilith is happy to give you a solo show!

girl_dialog: Hi! Are you interested in signing a new contract with the cute and charming succubus idol?
switch_1: Didn't you just sign it yesterday?
switch_2: I feel that there is a conspiracy...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Well... As hell's number one idol and Lucifer's leading pioneer, Lilith's recent performance is not enough!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Stop being suspicious! If you are willing to sign, Lilith is happy to give you a solo show!

girl_dialog: Do you like my bear? What do you think of animals like bears?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: The power of nature is always worthy of trust and reliance. She can fight better than me on the battlefield!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, on the battlefield, many enemies said the same before being stunned by her!

girl_dialog: Do you like my bear? What do you think of animals like bears?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: The power of nature is always worthy of trust and reliance. She can fight better than me on the battlefield!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Well, on the battlefield, many enemies said the same before being stunned by her!

girl_dialog: Will I be a hero who will save the world in the future?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hum...Look at this awakening power. Sooner or later I will become the leader recognized by my companions!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Why I feel that you have no confidence in me. Do you want me to give you a punch to prove it? !

girl_dialog: Alas... Does the war between the gods for thousands of years make sense?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It seems that there is no difference between gods and humans. Heroes will also fight to implement the correct ideas.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I think so too. Instead of wasting time fighting every day, I'd rather sit down and have a cup of black tea and play poker games.

girl_dialog: Well... if I'm the same as Bari... and wear a witch costume... how do you think of it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: What are you talking about! Wait, where are you looking at? ! I'm going to be angry! !
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I think so too! The witch costume is a symbol of justice and elegance!

girl_dialog: Do you like playing baseball? Are you interested in competing with me?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Humph! After solving the monster's troubles at the moment, I am looking forward to competing with you on the court!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: At least you are definitely not as strong as me in hitting. The broken windows in the classroom are all my masterpieces of home runs!

girl_dialog: In the face of powerful monsters, sometimes I have to use bows and arrows to fight... How can I shoot more accurately?
switch_2: Wear a good pair of glasses?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You... why are you staring at my breasts? ! That does not affect my bow!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Humph! My eyes are not bad at all. It is not a problem to throw an apple with a knife within ten meters!

girl_dialog: I miss the days when I played a game of beach volleyball happily in the hot summer.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Haha! Youth are valuable on the field and on the beach!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: What you said is really direct... Well, though I am confident about my figure...

girl_dialog: Death is not an end, but a new beginning... What do you think?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: There is no need to doubt that everyone who has left the world will always meet again in another way.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Haha...When you leave this world, maybe you will understand...

girl_dialog: If you can choose, what do you want, eternal life or a happy life?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: This was also my choice, but after witnessing countless farewells, all I have left is loneliness...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: That is quite an interesting answer. As human beings, life is like fireworks-short but brilliant.

girl_dialog: What do you think of the heavy fate carried by the heroes?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oh, it feels like you and I are so similar. Maybe you also have a little string in my fate?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Huh... It's fun to watch human beings struggle helplessly in front of an unchangeable destiny...

girl_dialog: Hum... Guess what your luck is today?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Heehee... Staying with me, a girl in charge of bad luck, can at least protect you from bad luck.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Heehee...If you don't throw away the banana skin after eating the banana, you should be able to dodge a bullet...

girl_dialog: Is there a girl you like? Would you like me, a genius prophet, to help you predict your relationship with her?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Let me see who you like...Wow! You are such a bold person!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah, destiny tells me that you will like a cute girl with cat ears and she likes sleeping late...

girl_dialog: Well... I'm used to the fate of being treated with cold eyes because of constantly predicting disasters.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I am not so feeble! But... But if you want to comfort me, I'll make a change to let you hug me!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Wow... it's rare that you can say such artistic words, it surprised me...

girl_dialog: Awww... The weather is nice today. Are you interested in basking with me?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I know a good place to bask in the sun! But I have to ask first, are you... scared of heights?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Get used to it a few more times! Don't you want to have healthy tan skin?

girl_dialog: Eh...? I feel a hot gaze on me...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Come on, don't be so shy... Appreciating the beautiful figure of Egyptian girls is a kind of enjoyment!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Really? ! Nuit thinks so too! In return, give you a kiss! Chu!

girl_dialog: The dry desert occasionally has a downpour, which is really refreshing!
switch_2: Holding an umbrella is a bit troublesome...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: My desert also longs for a gentle rain tonight...so...are you free tonight?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Umbrellas are too boring! Don't you think that a girl soaked in the rain is a kind of beauty?

girl_dialog: The beauty of art lies in who appreciates it. Don't you think so?
switch_2: I don't know much about art.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It's easy to get thousands of money but hard to find a truly friend. Maybe my art exists for you...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If you are willing to stay with me forever, you will understand sooner or later...

girl_dialog: This world is the most beautiful artwork. May it not be destroyed by war...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Perhaps it is, the good and bad are ever-changing. Without the cruelty of war, how can the peace come...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: After this disaster is over, I will go around the world with you to restore this artwork.

girl_dialog: The universe is unconscious; it regards everyone as insignificant. Do you agree with ​​this sentence?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Sometimes I sigh for the mercilessness of heaven and earth, but this is also the rule of nature and it is hard to break...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Although I don't want to say that, kindness without power may just be weakness.

girl_dialog: What do you think of my music... and my character?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It seems that we are heart to heart. I always hope that I can be as gentle as the earth.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It seems that you can see the enthusiasm for art in my heart. Few people understand me like this.

girl_dialog: Are you interested in archery?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Are you? As the best archery of the Yamato god pedigree, it becomes more worthy to compete with you!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: After mastering the skills, it is very simple. If you are interested, I can teach you personally!

girl_dialog: Your age is really mysterious! I just saw someone talking in a box in a street shop!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Is that thing called TV? What kind of magic can lock people in boxes...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I thought it was a monster, so I shot it with one arrow... Why did you look at me and laugh! Did I do something stupid?

girl_dialog: Are you free tonight? Are you interested in watching a fireworks display with me together?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: That's really exciting! See you tonight! By the way, do you want me to prepare a yukata for you? !
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Humph... Are you going to date other girls? Your face is very red...

girl_dialog: Come on! I found something fun! Just press this button, it can record the scenery in front of you!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Ah! So this thing is called a camera... In terms of painting and recording, this thing is much useful than the magic!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Why are you suddenly facing me... It's too sudden! Wait wait wait! I need to change into a more beautiful kimono!

girl_dialog: Everyone is eager to predict their own destiny, but do they have the courage to face the cruelty of fate?
switch_1: At least I have the courage.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? But it's a pity that you are not an ordinary mortal or an ordinary god, even I can't predict your future.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: In fact, whether you are a mortal or a god, knowing your own destiny is not necessarily a good thing.

girl_dialog: As the goddess of fate, I cannot remember my past, nor can I know who I am...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Are you referring to the three sisters of Nornir in Norse? Possibly, I feel that there are fragments of their souls in my body...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: The three sisters of Moirai in Greece? Maybe...I feel that sometimes they appear in dreams...

girl_dialog: Do you like drinking tea? I miss the peaceful afternoon tea time every day before the end of the world...
switch_2: I don't like it very much...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: After this disaster is over, I really hope to have the opportunity to enjoy the afternoon tea and snacks with you...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It seems that you might be more suitable for this adventurous age when there are wars than a peaceful period...

girl_dialog: Do you like drinking tea? I miss the peaceful afternoon tea time every day before the end of the world...
switch_2: I don't like it very much...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: After this disaster is over, I really hope to have the opportunity to enjoy the afternoon tea and snacks with you...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It seems that you might be more suitable for this adventurous age when there are wars than a peaceful period...

girl_dialog: Even though I was once one of the strongest gods of Yamato god pedigree, I would lose my divine power, which is really pitiful...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: From ancient times to the present, most mortals would only ask me for help, and I never thought that there would be a day when I need help from a mortal...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah...Really? Then your fate is responsible for retrieving my lost divine power with me.

girl_dialog: What are mortals and what are gods? Does it really make sense to discuss these boring titles?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? I feel that these so-called titles and identities have no effect other than triggering a war between the gods...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Yes. It is better to do something meaningful when you have time to discuss these things, such as... have a date with someone you like?

girl_dialog: In fact, country, throne, and theocracy are all worthless to me nowadays...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Because eventually these worldly things will usher in death, and the netherworld is the only eternal destination.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh? So if one day, I hope you give up everything that is mundane for me, what choice would you make?

girl_dialog: What do you think...is the most valuable thing in this world?
switch_2: I think it should be love?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Maybe you are right. I like the strong, especially those who are stronger than me and make me feel safe...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Love is a romantic lie that most people talk casually, but you make me feel a warmth that I have never had before.

girl_dialog: What kind of girls do you like?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hey...does it take so long to think about it? Or... I am not attractive enough in your eyes?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh dear... are you talking about me? Although I like straightforward people, being too straightforward is not romantic enough!

girl_dialog: Why are you always distracted when chatting with me recently? Is there anything on your mind?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? Let me guess, um... you have a virus called love, and there is no cure for it!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Emmm...is...is it a girl you like?

girl_dialog: Do you like small animals? Which kind do you prefer, puppies or kittens?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I thought you were more interested in dogs! I also like cats very much, but I am weak to their changeable personality...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Really? ! I especially like Shiba Inu! They are gentle, smart, and lively, you will always be in a great mood with them!

girl_dialog: As a god in charge of love and marriage, who do you think is better, Cupid or me?
switch_1: I presume you are the one.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Aha! I think so too! Cupid is too casual in her treatment of people and their fate! Love can't be a joke!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Awwwwww... I didn't expect that you are so gentle. Even if you think Cupid is better, I won't be angry!

girl_dialog: War is also fate. Two opponents whose fate is not staggered will not stand on the same battlefield.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: No,I don't hate. I have seen a lot of duels on the battlefield, and have also seen romances born after these duels...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmph, I see the thread that binds you to the girls... It's so complicated that it's almost forming a net..oh my gosh...

girl_dialog: Even if I want to repair the damage caused by the war as much as possible, it is difficult for me to do it after losing my divine power.
switch_1: I will do my best to help you.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: This is a long journey, but I would love to have your company.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are right. As far as the earth is concerned, no matter how many injuries it is, it will slowly heal over time.

girl_dialog: Even if I want to repair the damage caused by the war as much as possible, it is difficult for me to do it after losing my divine power.
switch_1: I will do my best to help you.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: This is a long journey, but I would love to have your company.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are right. As far as the earth is concerned, no matter how many injuries it is, it will slowly heal over time.

girl_dialog: Sunny days are the best! I love basking in the sun under a cloudless sky.
switch_1: You seem to be in a good mood.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes, especially after enjoying the afternoon sun with someone like you. How could it get any better?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Mmm... Are you suggesting that I wear even less clothing when basking in order to cool off?

girl_dialog: Cats are kept in many temples in Egypt, not only because they are cute, but also as a sacred symbol.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Let's open a cat-themed café together after this war is over!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Yes, in some Egyptian legends, cats are messengers of gods, and some can also become cute girls!

girl_dialog: Those who uphold justice will always emerge victorious!
switch_1: Were you just talking to yourself?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oops! Where did you come from? I... I was just practicing some lines from a drama!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ah... I like that! It's the perfect line to shout after defeating a powerful enemy!

girl_dialog: Who do you think is more attractive, me or the goddess of the sky, Nuit?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hmph! Indeed, Nuit possesses a lot power and charm among ...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It's rare to see you hesitate. Why don't you visit my room tonight and let me reveal the correct answer.

girl_dialog: Just as the sun falls behind the horizon, even a god must eventually fade away.
switch_1: It's rare to see you so depressed…
girl_dialog_after_switch1: As the main god of Egypt, I should not show any weakness in front of my companions. It was a only a private lament that I shared with you.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I would like that! Hugging you as the sun sets is the best comfort imaginable.

girl_dialog: Do you like Egyptian style clothing?
switch_2: Can't you tell by how I look at you?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? Indeed, compared to other clothing, this style is the best at revealing a girl's skin and figure.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Normally, I'm not good at guessing, but the fire in your eyes tells me all I need to know...

girl_dialog: Justice or evil is just an excuse. It is the strength of the power that determines the world.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Actually... I quite agree with you as my commander, at least you are a strong enough commander!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If others answer this way, I will definitely beat him up, but at least you have proved your insistence on justice with your actions.

girl_dialog: Justice or evil is just an excuse. It is the strength of the power that determines the world.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Actually... I quite agree with you as my commander, at least you are a strong enough commander!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If others answer this way, I will definitely beat him up, but at least you have proved your insistence on justice with your actions.

girl_dialog: No matter what kind of disaster the world has encountered, one should never give up his belief in pursuing justice and light!
switch_2: This is not easy to do.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: This is the excellent quality needed as a commander of the gods! As your companion, I am proud of you.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: There is no need to doubt yourself, even if you really fall into the abyss, I will always be with you.

girl_dialog: I never advocate solving problems by means of war, but I also never fear to end disputes by war!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Well, it isn't. Justice without power cannot fight against darkness, and tolerance does not mean indulging without principles.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: As a mortal, I am quite surprised that you can realize this truth, and your wisdom is worthy of appreciation.

girl_dialog: I have been wondering whether it is right to cooperate with demons in order to defeat stronger enemies.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I had met with Lucifer on the battlefield once. Although her behavior was not justified, she was unexpectedly principled.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You are right, at least Michael, Raphael, and Gabriel will not agree to this easily.

girl_dialog: It's been a while since I met you. As your mentor, it's a relief to witness your growth.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Haha... At least the time we were together was much more interesting than when I was alone.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Of course, I don't want to see you on the battlefield like a rookie, being beaten by the enemy then fly away tens of meters...

girl_dialog: You ask me why I always carry a lantern during the day? It seems that you don't understand my duty as a witch...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: As a witch who is in charge of life and death, I not only guide the living creatures, but also need to illuminate the path for the dead.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: This lantern illuminates the road to the underworld. Thanks to it, we can avoid a lot of monsters and troubles.

girl_dialog: No matter what road you finally choose, I hope you will not hesitate to make your choice.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oh? Regardless of whether you can do or not, at least your current momentum is quite strong, I bet you can at least hold on for... a month?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: If you hesitate, you will lose. This is from a legendary Japanese swordsman. Well... I guess you might have heard it...

girl_dialog: In fact, sometimes I wondered, what kind of identity should I use to face you...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Ah...It really made me feel a little bit disappointed. I thought you would give me a bolder answer...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Ahhhhh...it would be too unromantic to tell you directly. How about coming to my room tonight?

girl_dialog: The earth is the source of life. Even if I lose most of my divine power, the earth will give me strength again.
switch_2: Do you want to regain the divine power?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Time is the best medicine to cure the earth. I only hope that this war can end as soon as possible.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It doesn't matter. The earth will always take something from me and give it to a more suitable person.

girl_dialog: I don't approve of Nuit fighting along side of us, even if doomsday is upon us.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I fear she won't take our struggle seriously. She has also caused more trouble in Egypt than she has ever solved.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: She is indeed good at strength, but as the commander, you will soon realize that she doesn't quite understand what a command is...

girl_dialog: The king is always lonely. This is the only real feeling after I ruled the Nordic gods for so long.
switch_1: I don't care about being lonely.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You are still too young. Only when you become the ruler recognized by the gods can you truly understand the meaning of loneliness.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Interesting. I have seen countless kings, and no one has ever said that. You are indeed a unique commander.

girl_dialog: It is the bounden duty of the rulers of Norse to protect the world tree, but this is not an easy task.
switch_2: I will try my best to help you.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It is the pillar of this Nordic country. As a former king, I miss the feeling of standing on the top of a tree and looking down on everything...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Few humans will give me such a firm answer, maybe you can really become the leader of the gods.

girl_dialog: I was defeated in the doomsday of Ragnarok. I hope that this kind of thing will never happen again.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hmph...If other people say this, I will only think that he is a fool, but I agree with your ability and wisdom.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: This is a bet that risking life, but I believe that with you, there is no enemy that can make us fear.

girl_dialog: Wisdom is the guarantee of victory. We need not only unmatched brave men in the war, but also clever military counsellors.
switch_1: It's hard to be a wise man...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I was willing to pay the price of one eye in order to gain wisdom, but I understand that the wise man will always be invincible.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I used to be the ruler of the gods, but you are the future of the gods. I hope you can hold this glory for me.

girl_dialog: To be honest, in the eyes of other gods, I was just an unromantic and indifferent ruler...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: It seems that the times have changed. Now, as a companion of the gods, it is indeed easier for me to get close to others than as the commander of the gods.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Really? It seems that someone deserves to spend a night on me and entertain him with a good bottle of mead.

girl_dialog: Is the charm of the songs I sing really powerful enough to make people throw themselves into the sea...
switch_1: At least the legend said it is...
switch_2: Actually I want to hear it!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: This is really distressing! My ideal is to be an idol!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh, really? ! To prevent accidents, should I find a rope to trap you on the mast?

girl_dialog: I really want to see the scenery on the land. I heard that there are beautiful grasslands and majestic mountains on the land...
switch_2: I thought you could come ashore.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Yes, doomsday is not over yet, I don't want to see erupting volcanoes and dusty ruins.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Of course I can go ashore, the premise is that you can hold me, haha...

girl_dialog: I heard that Lord Poseidon lost most of her divine power when she woke up in this world. Is this true?
switch_2: Do you want to play a prank?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: So that's true! This is so exciting...ah no no no.. so regrettable...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Haha! How could I? I just want to see the face of the god of the sea who is majestic in the past...

girl_dialog: I will not feel sad about the disasters that the earth has suffered in the war, this is just a necessary test.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Everything follows the rules of nature. There is no need to avoid fate. The tribulation will make the earth more solid.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: No, I won't. Everything is endless and cyclical. Even if it is silent for a while, it will eventually be reborn on the earth.

girl_dialog: During the time I got along with you, I felt more like your elders than companions.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: So no matter what trouble you encounter, please tell me. At least I should face it with you.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmm... It seems that in your eyes, I am much younger than I thought...

girl_dialog: As a mortal, you have to carry the heavy responsibility of solving this disaster. Fate is too harsh on you...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: 你有着和我一样坚强的意志和灵魂，希望众神能在你的统率下度过这场浩劫……
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Indeed. No matter how strong a person is, he may not have enough reliable companions.

girl_dialog: Which do you like better, flowers or trees? After each battle, I always plant various plants on the battlefield.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Even the simplest flower can use its unique fragrance to dispel the dark clouds of war.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Trees are a sign of recovery. Even they are not beautiful as flowers, they can slowly heal the scars of the earth.

girl_dialog: When I was summoned into this world, I lost most of my divine power, which I have to say is a pity...
switch_1: Do you want to regain your divine power?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Of course, if I were to return to the heyday of divine power, then end this doomsday... I am afraid it will only take a few days.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: 安心吧，我并不会因此而消沉，在见证你的成长后，我已经看见了新的希望。

girl_dialog: Minotaur's labyrinth... is it really so easy to get out of it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Ah...really? ! I will throw you into the center of the labyrinth tomorrow to see if this is true.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: In fact, if you have the power as orc, you can destroy walls when you face them, and sooner or later you can get out.

girl_dialog: Minotaur's labyrinth... is it really so easy to get out of it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Ah...really? ! I will throw you into the center of the labyrinth tomorrow to see if this is true.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: In fact, if you have the power as orc, you can destroy walls when you face them, and sooner or later you can get out.

girl_dialog: In order to pursue your own ideas, one chooses to sacrifice. Do you think it is worthy?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Few humans will give me such a firm answer, maybe you can really become the leader of the gods.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Find an idea worthy of sacrifice. Whether you are confused or fearful, I will always guard you.

girl_dialog: In order to pursue your own ideas, one chooses to sacrifice. Do you think it is worthy?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Few humans will give me such a firm answer, maybe you can really become the leader of the gods.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Find an idea worthy of sacrifice. Whether you are confused or fearful, I will always guard you.

girl_dialog: Hi, what do you think of the idea of combining the real world and dreams into one?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Haha...Always immersed in dreams, dreams are reality, is there anything more wonderful than this...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmph, what an unromantic guy, at least I have dreams.

girl_dialog: Do you think... I can become a strong person that my companions can rely on?
switch_2: At least in dreams you can.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: For me, this is really not easy...but with you, maybe I can change myself.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Then in order to make this dream come true, it seems that people all over the world will never be able to wake up.

girl_dialog: Do you think it is worth doing whatever it takes, in order to become stronger?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Ok, is it? But only the strong can control the destiny of himself and the world, is that right?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: There is no difference between good and evil in the world. Maybe kindness is only defined by the strong...

girl_dialog: If you have the ability to read people's mind, would you want to secretly read the thoughts of the person you like?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You're right. What's the point if gained love by this kind of ability?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh, what an honest and cute guy! Then tell me honestly...what are you thinking about now?

girl_dialog: If you have the ability to read people's mind, would you want to secretly read the thoughts of the person you like?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You're right. What's the point if gained love by this kind of ability?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Oh, what an honest and cute guy! Then tell me honestly...what are you thinking about now?

girl_dialog: I'm bored! How about sparring with me? It will be good practice!
switch_2: It seems someone is calling me!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Haha! I won't lose like last time! Take that!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hey! Not that excuse again! Ah... Forget it! I'll practice alone with a combat dummy.

girl_dialog: Flames... they are both beautiful and dangerous. What do you think of them?
switch_1: Fire is the symbol of civilization.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Exactly. Fire was the first great discovery, and now civilization thrives on it.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Perhaps. The flame brings wisdom, but it also ignites disputes in the kingdom and the desire to plunder...

girl_dialog: I prefer to solve things by fighting. I hate it when humans try to reason with me instead.
switch_1: Sometimes a fight does solve the problem.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Exactly! Troublesome people just need a good punch. If that's not enough... uh... then two punches!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I'm too hot-tempered to reason. But every time, you manage to calm me down.

girl_dialog: Do you like spicy food?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: There is nothing better than a big bowl of rice topped with chili peppers and roast meat just before battle!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hmm... But girls who like hot are always popular! Whether it's character or figure...

girl_dialog: Hi, what do you think of this mummy-style costume?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You have really good taste! Do you want to come to my room and...let me teach you how to dress...?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It's troublesome to wrap it around, but it's very convenient to take it off! Do you want to try it?

girl_dialog: Hi, what do you think of this mummy-style costume?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You have really good taste! Do you want to come to my room and...let me teach you how to dress...?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It's troublesome to wrap it around, but it's very convenient to take it off! Do you want to try it?

girl_dialog: Are you looking forward to having eternal youth, like the gods?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Youth is an invaluable wealth. No matter appearance, vitality or passion, it is meaningful with youth!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: No way? ! I have never seen a mortal who does not long for eternal youth!

girl_dialog: Do you think the precious golden apple... will really trigger a war between the gods?
switch_1: At least in Greece it will.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Haha, I heard that the goddesses Athena, Hera, and Aphrodite are fighting hard for this!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: You think it won't? ! Let's make a bet. I think of a funny prank, hee hee...

girl_dialog: If I were a mortal, my beauty would fade away by the passing time, can I still be in love?
switch_1: At least I can give you love.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You didn't lie to me, did you? If you lie to me, I will never forgive you!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: That's right... Most often mortals' love will disappear with the passing of youth.

girl_dialog: Abundant music and beautiful poetry, which art do you prefer?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Music is the soul of a song. Are you interested in listening to me sing a song?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Poetry can always express people's emotions well. Would you like to see my new poetry?

girl_dialog: Abundant music and beautiful poetry, which art do you prefer?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Music is the soul of a song. Are you interested in listening to me sing a song?
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Poetry can always express people's emotions well. Would you like to see my new poetry?

girl_dialog: Humph... I smell something I like! You brought fish, right? !
switch_1: Your have such a sensitive nose...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: If you are willing to exchange with me, I will give you an extraordinary gift!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Awww, you are such a liar! If you don't give it to me, I will scratch you!

girl_dialog: Are human beings afraid of whatever monsters they see...?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oh! ! Did you say I'm so cute, right? ! It must be so! !
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hum, I will sneak into your bedroom tonight and eat you, be careful miaow...

girl_dialog: Hey! Do humans like to call themselves the master of cats? What does the word master mean?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? ! How about next time I invite you to a party with animal monster friends? !
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Miaow...Is it the kind of shy relationship that makes people blush...You are really direct meow...

girl_dialog: Ears and tails are rare treasures! Do you want to touch it?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Well, if you are willing to give me fish, then I'll allow you to touch meow!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I never thought who could hold back our furry temptation strikes! Are you really a human meow? !

girl_dialog: Ah... Whether it's a god or a human, everyone seems to have a selfish side.
switch_1: But gods are immortal, and humans are not.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? Although I did see a lot of good people before I became a monster...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Alas...it's a shame to have fish but don't know how to share it with friends miaow...

girl_dialog: As a demon cat, do you think my power is strong?
switch_2: How do you feel about yourself?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Is it? ! Humph! I will definitely become your most reliable comrade miaow! !
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I think I'm strong miaow. Such a big stone can be crushed with just one paw!

girl_dialog: I have never expected that I, once one of the strongest gods, would lose power like a mortal...
switch_1: Do you want to regain power?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: I must end this catastrophe with you and regain the divine power that originally belonged to me!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: I should also be grateful for this destiny. If it weren't like this, I wouldn't meet you...

girl_dialog: Do you like surfing?
switch_1: I am very good at surfing!
switch_2: Eh, I will be drowning in water.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Really? I have never seen a human being able to beat me, and I must compete with you if I have a chance!
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Do you want me to teach you surfing? I will hold you tight, at least you don't have to worry about sinking to the bottom...
